															<span class="parameter">
									<p>Options to be used when generating the checkbox <code>&lt;input /&gt;</code> element:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>'checked'</code> <em>boolean</em>: Whether or not the field should be checked by default.</li>
<li><code>'value'</code> <em>mixed</em>: if specified, it will be used as the 'value' html
attribute and no hidden input field will be added.</li>
<li>Any other options specified are rendered as HTML attributes of the element.</li>
</ul>
